snippet.title: Jawan: Chaleya (Hindi) | Shah Rukh Khan | Nayanthara | Atlee | Anirudh | Arijit S, Shilpa R | Kumaar
snippet.description:
Witness the love with Chaleya, presenting the second song from the highly-awaited film Jawan directed by Atlee. The film stars Shah Rukh Khan, Vijay Sethupathi, Nayanthara, and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance) and is set to release in cinemas on 7th September 2023 in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu!

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu ||Something Missamma Episode 06 || Pre Wedding || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Something Missamma Episode 06 Pre Wedding MCM
Filmymoji releases its new episode of Missamma series where Middle class Madhu will be forced to assist Penta Reddy in chopping someone’s hand off. Meanwhile Dupesh lands in jammalamadugu and proposes to take a pre-wedding shoot of bulli Guvva and Sravani. The broker introduces the alliance as a Dubai return and Madhu blackmails him for money for not revealing this narrative. Dupesh takes out bride and the groom along with MCM and Komali for the pre-wedding shoot and instead of taking pictures he convinces bulli Guvva to click his pictures with the bride. Watch the full episode to find out the shocking truth which Dupesh reveals about the marriage and whether NaatuGuntala gang finds out about the whereabouts of Madhu.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 31 Teaser - 14th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

Thimiru  is a 2006 Indian Tamil-language action film written and directed by Tarun Gopi in his directorial debut. It stars Vishal, Reema Sen, Sriya Reddy, I. M. Vijayan, Manoj K. Jayan and Vadivelu, while Kiran Rathod makes a cameo appearance. The film's score and soundtrack are composed by Yuvan Shankar Raja. Produced by Vikram Krishna, under the banner of G K Film Corporation, Thimiru was released on 4 August 2006 and became one of the top-grossing Tamil films in 2006.

snippet.title: Madhavi ने Bhide को चाय नहीं अचार बनाने का दिया Order |Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah|Unknown Guest
snippet.description:
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Madhavi and Bhide are in a hurry to pack pickles and papads for their customers. Bhide is waiting for tea but Madhavi explains to him about urgent delivery. Bhide calls Madhavi a home minister then Madhavi orders him to focus on pickles and Papad not on the tea. Stay tuned for more. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 2726
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal #shahrukh_khan #kajol #shahrukh 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of Unknown Guest:

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3849 | 14 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3849: Independence Day Plans
--------------------------------------------------------
Nattu Kaka and Bagha call Jetha to inform him that money has been taken in their hamlet and they require assistance. Jetha instantly sends money to them, and Champaklal condemns the event, questioning how someone could steal money from a holy location. Tapu plans a trip with his friends but fails to notify Jetha. Later, Bagha and Nattu Kaka devise a special program for the Gada store's consumers. What exactly is the plan at Gada Electronics?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3849, 14 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

Préparez-vous pour l'épreuve de rire ultime alors que nous réunissons le combo le plus fou de famille et d'amis dans le défi "Hasna Mana Hai" ! 😂
Qui craquera le premier et éclatera de rires incontrôlables ?

Ruchi et Piyush
Des vidéos amusantes pour toute la famille. Les personnages principaux sont Ruchi, Piyush, Belle-mère, Aide ménagère, Aayu et Pihu. La langue de la vidéo est l'hindi. snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2│Flowers│EP# 313
snippet.description:
അമ്മമാരില്ലാത്ത വീട്ടിൽ അച്ഛന്മാരുടെ വിളയാട്ടം!! പക്ഷെ കുട്ടിപ്പട്ടാളത്തോട് പിടിച്ചുനിൽക്കാൻ അത്ര എളുപ്പമായിരിക്കില്ല. ഉപ്പും മുളകും വീട്ടിൽ ഇനി എന്തുനടക്കുമെന്ന് കണ്ടറിഞ്ഞ് കാണാം... 

'Uppum Mulakum' is the favorite sitcom of Malayalees. The show, which travels through Balu, Neelu and their four children's lives. This show brings the humor, emotions and problems of a middle-class family's daily life to the audience in an interesting way. We will have to wait and see what will happen in 'Uppum Mulakum'?



#uppummulakum  ​#BijuSopanam #NishaSarang

snippet.description:
#arshfam #arsheen #damnfam 
Tumhari bhabhi fir aa he gayi mumbai 🥹🫰 
Jab b yasmeen ko milta hu i feel something different in me and suddenly sab slow sa hojata hae usko dekh kr idk why 😂 - meet new arshfam 
Baki toh bohat ghumna firna kiya mumbai pura dikhaeya yaasu ko and bohat sari memories bnai ekathe 🫰 

Rishu ka b birthday bnaeya road trip b hogya pack your bags b hogya baki yeh vlog toh bohat soecial rahega mereliye puri zindagi 🫰 

Baki toh kuch ni bas insta peh krlo mera broadcast join 😂 - arshfam ki fam

Sirf Tum Mega Episode 31 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Hamza Sohail - Mohsin Abbas Haider - 13th Aug 2023 - Har Pal Geo

"Sirf Tum" revolves around Abeer who has recently returned from abroad to live with her extended family. Abeer's perspective on life and her priorities are different from her family's, which leads to conflict between them. Her cousins, Hanan and Hamza, are also part of this extended family.

Hamza is a rebellious and unconventional person who dreams of living life without any responsibilities or restrictions. In contrast, Hanan is a mature and sensible man who believes in love and relationships. After a series of events, Abeer and Hamza are set to marry. However, Hamza's inappropriate demands and unreasonable behaviour towards Abeer cause her to back out from the wedding. This creates chaos in the family and creates tension between Hamza & Abeer.
Ultimately, Hanan and Abeer are forced to marry each other. Though they reluctantly start their new life together, their past traumas continue to haunt them. The question remains: will Hanan and Abeer be able to overcome their past and find love for each other? Or will their differences and past experiences lead to further conflict and separation?

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3848: Time Par Order Ready
--------------------------------------------------------
Madhavi has received a big order of tomato pickles to be delivered, but the cylinder at Bhide's house goes out of gas. Tapu Sena assists Bhide in getting a new cylinder from Jetha's place, Tapu Sena brings the cylinder to Bhide's place. Madhavi successfully cooks and prepares the pickle order and packs it for the customer. Later, the customer being grateful for the order asks Madhavi to charge him as per the current price of the tomatoes. Watch the episode to know more.  

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3848, 12 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Jiya Shankar admits feelings for Abhishek Malhan, slams Pooja Bhatt; says Elvish has a heart of gold
snippet.description:
Jiya Shankar, who recently got eliminated from Bigg Boss OTT season 2 and couldn't be a part of Top 5 spoke to ETimes TV about her journey in the show. She shared that she would not like to meet Jad Hadid and Avinash Sachdev after the show and also revealed the reason behind the same. Reacting to her fight with Pooja Bhatt, Jiya slammed the Dil Hai Ke Maanta Nahin actress for saying that she won't get work in the industry. She further spoke about her special bond with Abhishek Malhan and admitted to having feelings for him and a special place in her heart. Jiya got emotional talking about Abhishek Malhan's close ones commenting on her character but also shared that if Abhishek is willing she would take their bond ahead. She also opened up about her equation with her father and why she would never go back to him.  

#jiyashankar  #biggbossott #biggbossottseason2 #elvishyadav #abhishekmalhan #fukrainsaan

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Revisit The Journey: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

snippet.title: 12th Fail Official Teaser | Vidhu Vinod Chopra | Vikrant Massey | 27th October 2023
snippet.description:
प्रिय विद्यार्थी,

आपको ध्यान होगा कि करीब 4 साल पहले दृष्टि संस्थान के पूर्व विद्यार्थी मनोज कुमार शर्मा (IPS) के तैयारी के दिनों से जुड़े संघर्षों पर 'ट्वेल्थ फेल' नामक उपन्यास प्रकाशित हुआ था। इसमें दृष्टि की ही विद्यार्थी श्रद्धा जोशी (IRS) की कहानी भी थी जो मनोज की जीवनसंगिनी हैं। उपन्यास दृष्टि के ही पूर्व विद्यार्थी अनुराग पाठक (जॉइंट कमिश्नर, GST) ने लिखा था और भूमिका लिखी थी विकास सर ने!

अब इसी उपन्यास पर 27 अक्तूबर को एक बड़ी फिल्म आ रही है जिसके लेखक, निर्माता और निर्देशक श्री विधु विनोद चोपड़ा हैं! थ्री इडियट्स, मुन्नाभाई एमबीबीएस, पीके, 1942 : ए लव स्टोरी जैसी फिल्मों के निर्माता रहे श्री विधु विनोद चोपड़ा ने लगभग 4 साल के कठोर परिश्रम से यह फ़िल्म बनाई है।

फ़िल्म में मनोज शर्मा की भूमिका प्रसिद्ध अभिनेता विक्रांत मैसी निभा रहे हैं। विकास सर की भूमिका में खुद विकास सर ही हैं!

यह इस फ़िल्म का टीज़र है। आप भी देखिये।

=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵

localized.title: 12th Fail Official Teaser | Vidhu Vinod Chopra | Vikrant Massey | 27th October 2023
localized.description:
प्रिय विद्यार्थी,

आपको ध्यान होगा कि करीब 4 साल पहले दृष्टि संस्थान के पूर्व विद्यार्थी मनोज कुमार शर्मा (IPS) के तैयारी के दिनों से जुड़े संघर्षों पर 'ट्वेल्थ फेल' नामक उपन्यास प्रकाशित हुआ था। इसमें दृष्टि की ही विद्यार्थी श्रद्धा जोशी (IRS) की कहानी भी थी जो मनोज की जीवनसंगिनी हैं। उपन्यास दृष्टि के ही पूर्व विद्यार्थी अनुराग पाठक (जॉइंट कमिश्नर, GST) ने लिखा था और भूमिका लिखी थी विकास सर ने!

अब इसी उपन्यास पर 27 अक्तूबर को एक बड़ी फिल्म आ रही है जिसके लेखक, निर्माता और निर्देशक श्री विधु विनोद चोपड़ा हैं! थ्री इडियट्स, मुन्नाभाई एमबीबीएस, पीके, 1942 : ए लव स्टोरी जैसी फिल्मों के निर्माता रहे श्री विधु विनोद चोपड़ा ने लगभग 4 साल के कठोर परिश्रम से यह फ़िल्म बनाई है।

फ़िल्म में मनोज शर्मा की भूमिका प्रसिद्ध अभिनेता विक्रांत मैसी निभा रहे हैं। विकास सर की भूमिका में खुद विकास सर ही हैं!

यह इस फ़िल्म का टीज़र है। आप भी देखिये।

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: Gadar 2 का गदर प्रीमियर, बेटे Sunny Deol की फिल्म देखने पहुंचीं Prakash Kaur, Bobby बीवी के साथ आए
snippet.description:
सनी देओल की फिल्म गदर 2 सिनेमाघरों में गदर मचा रही है। तो ऐसा ही गदर बीती रात फिल्म के धमाकेदार प्रीमियर में भी नज़र आया । गदर 2 के रिलीज़ होते ही फिल्म के मेकर्स ने बीते दिन फिल्म का स्टारस्टडिड प्रीमियर होस्ट किया गया, जहां फिल्म को लेकर लोगों की दीवानगी और क्रेज़ साफ नज़र आया। 22 साल पाकिस्तान की बैंड बजाने तारा सिंह फिर दोबारा बॉर्डर पार पहुंचा है, तो तारा की दहाड़ सुनने बॉलीवुड भी खींचा चला आया।

snippet.description:
🎥 Join us for an exclusive interview with Jiya Shankar, the recent evictee from Bigg Boss OTT 2! In this candid conversation, Jiya opens up about her unforgettable moments inside the house. She shares heartwarming insights into her special bond with Abhishek Malhan, along with hilarious anecdotes from the soap water fiasco with Elvish. 🛁

But that's not all! Jiya spills the beans on her connections with fellow housemates - from her deep camaraderie with Pooja Bhatt and bebika Manisha, to the heartwarming story of her reconciliation with her friend Palak Purswani. 🤝 Get ready to dive into the emotional rollercoaster of Jiya's journey in the Bigg Boss house, filled with laughter, tears, and unforgettable memories. Iyer and Babita are in the sweet shop buying sweets for everyone in Gokuldham Society. Bbabita wants to give a party to everyone but Iyer tells next year with another promotion he will give the party.

#comedy2023 #comedy #jethalal #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Iyer Ka Promotion https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of TMKOC - Iyer Ka Promotion https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSkLfD49YxG8YsjmWdKNU0r

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3847 | 11 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3847: Gas Bich Mien Hui Khatam
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu Sena assists Bhide in carrying the enormous basket of 40 kilograms of tomatoes inside the house, and Goli requests a tomato as a sign of thanks. Bhide cheerfully presents him with a plump red tomato as a symbol of appreciation. Madhvi is relieved that she can finally begin preparing her pickle for the order. Sonu and Bhide are munching on Madhvi's homemade "besan ladoos" when they hear Madhvi's voice. The father and daughter run to the kitchen to check on her and discover that a petrol cylinder needs to be fuelled this time. Bhide hurries to Sodhi's residence to acquire a replacement cylinder, but he uses a different firm. Is Madhvi going to be able to deliver the pickles on time?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3847, 11 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: OMG 2 movie review | Akshay Kumar, Pankaj Tripathi, Yami Gautam | Honest Review
snippet.description:
OMG 2 is a 2023 Indian Hindi-language satirical comedy-drama film written and directed by Amit Rai. It is a spiritual sequel to OMG – Oh My God! (2012). The film stars Akshay Kumar, Pankaj Tripathi and Yami Gautam in lead roles, along with Pavan Malhotra, Govind Namdev, Arun Govil, Brijendra Kala and others. The film revolves around the subject of sex education in Indian schools. The film was theatrically released on 11 August 2023.
